  "caveats": [
    "SELF-REFERENTIAL: the world model is BOTH simulator and state estimator -> this proves the DAgger MECHANISM in-harness, NOT the real off-road/safety rate. AlpaSim (photoreal, external) is required to confirm the rate (exp #4 in the planner-bottleneck synthesis).",
    "KINEMATIC harness has NO real road boundary -> off-road is APPROXIMATED as large lateral deviation@2s (proxy thresholds pre-registered; 2.0 m primary).",
    "n=12 local val eps (not the full 40). The cross-fit paired design (every eval window out-of-sample, shared-difficulty cancelled) is the robust part; absolute rates are wide.",
    "The bicycle + pure-pursuit are a HARNESS controller shared by all arms; its fidelity floor cancels in the paired deltas (open_bike floor ~0.45 m ADE@2s, imagination proof).",
    "A2 substitutes half its per-step data with on-policy states vs A1; the A2-vs-A1 paired block isolates the on-policy contribution from raw training effort."
  ],
